docs/generated/api/

# experiment run backups / partial-result snapshots
*.bak

# ---> Scala
*.class
*.log

# virtual machine crash logs, see http://www.java.com/en/download/help/error_hotspot.xml
hs_err_pid*

# latex stuff
*.aux
*.fdb_latexmk
*fls
*.out
*.synctex*